{"tid":1814020,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎學野睇下點樣支爆","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T14:02:17.000Z","uid":100155,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"804d10380adfa4f33a8de5902a3de09c3cafc59e","tid":1814020,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"45:01開始   當年美國點樣拖爆蘇聯，而宜家又可以點對付更醒目嘅中共。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yEZKkShjkoY?t=2701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyEZKkShjkoY%3Ft%3D2701&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=17c8a972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yEZKkShjkoY?t=2701</a> <br />\n<br />\n中共用香港+華爾街中資上市同基金集資，再用呢d無盡嘅錢補貼發展偷翻黎嘅技術砌翻美國。美國終於想斷中共資金鏈（用compliance同audit要求令中資企業喺華爾街開始收皮），中資同華爾街班友咪過黎香港玩囉，<br />\n然後香港將變成中共唯一主要資金鏈。然後你明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支爆？ ：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssFRDSW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssFRDSW.png&h=c5f26c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論點，支共倒台係現時最接近獲得自治/獨立主權嘅途徑。<br />\n<br />\n**不過面對不斷而來嘅清算、被自殺、白色恐怖、興建中嘅新疆嶺、同埋排山倒海嘅惡法，香港人仲有時間慢慢打持久戰嗎？** 何況時間一長、反抗意志亦會續漸消磨。<br />\n<br />\n所以要趁宜家天時地利人和，加速支共倒台，才能光復香港、獲得民主自治同主權。<br />\n加速支爆，全民有責<br />\n<br />\n【香 港 出 路 只 有 支 爆】（長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6fe07321cf90d80058424acbefa57974804380e","tid":1814020,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f43178762f05720dcff4a0f64991a173aa295a32","tid":1814020,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8083b3a8f5b054d568207c955d324f7751